arshield\'s specific revenue contribution. Investors cannot distinguish Starshield revenue from Starlink Mobile or other enterprise/government connectivity revenue within the aggregated Enterprise & Government line item. This absence of granular disclosure is analytically material given Starshield\'s strategic significance to the government business.\n\n{\n  "sources": [\n    {\n      "url": "https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1181412/000162828026036936/spaceexplorationtechnologi.htm",\n      "name": "SpaceX S-1 Registration Statement (filed May 20, 2026)"\n    }\n  ]\n}',
